org.gephi.io.generator.spi

Interface Generator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    LongTask

    public interface Generator
extends LongTask
    Define a generator, that is generating graph structure from a bunch of parameters.

    Extends LongTask to support tasks progress and cancellation.
